<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login / Register</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/logoo.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css">
</head>
<body class="noise">
    <div class="navbar">
        <img src="/assets/logo.png" alt="App logo" class="logo">
        <h2>DocuVault</h2>
    </div>


    <div class="toggle_box">
    <div class="Register_toggle toggle">Register</div>
    <div class="Login_toggle toggle">Login</div>
    </div>
    <div class="createAccount form">
        <form action="/register" method="post" class="form_create">
            <label for="">Create an Account</label>
            <input type="username" name="username" required placeholder="email" aria-required="true">
            <input type="password" name="password" required placeholder="password" required>
            <button type="submit" class="register">Register</button>
        </form>
      <div class="card social-block">
        <div class="card-body">
          <a class="btn btn-block" href="/auth/google" role="button">
            <i class="fab fa-google"></i>
            Sign Up with Google
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="loginAccount form">
        <form action="/login" method="post" class="form_reg">
            <label for="">Login into Account</label>
            <input type="username" name="username" required placeholder="email">
            <input type="password" name="password" required placeholder="password">
            <button type="submit" class="">Login</button>
        </form>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <a class="btn btn-block" href="/auth/google" role="button">
              <i class="fab fa-google"></i>
              Sign In with Google
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <% if(locals.data){ %>
    <div class="usermsg">
      <p><%= data %></p>
    </div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="developer-says">
      <img src="/assets/logoo.png" alt="">
    <p>
      Hey there! I’m Squirry, and let me give you a quick overview of this project. It was built by Subhojeet Prasad, with
      the main goal of creating something truly complex and robust on the backend. So, he put his focus into backend architecture and database design.
      Currently, this app handles critical queries using transaction management (preventing race conditions) and implements strong authentication mechanisms. 
      And honestly, what better way to learn
      authentication than by building a full RBAC system? :)
      Here’s something helpful: if you’d prefer not to register using your main email account, you can enter
      {<i>anything</i>@mail.com} and set up a password. Prasad has temporarily disabled strict email validation so that
      anyone can explore the project anonymously. (Of course, if this becomes a production-grade application, that
      flexibility might change.)
      Finally, if you’d like to connect with Prasad, you can reach him here:
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/subhojeetprasad/">LinkedIn</a> |
      <a href="https://github.com/Prasad1-S">GitHub</a> |
      <a href="mailto:subhojeetprasad123@gmail.com">Email</a>
      He’s open to collaborations and internship opportunities!
      Extra's: The favicon is just me hanging out on top of this Browser Tab.
      Please pardon any minor CSS inconsistencies when viewing on a mobile device.
    </p>
    </div>





    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>